  <description><![CDATA[<p>Newly built for Winter 2015/16, this modern 4 star hotel will offer personalised, relaxed service and stylish accommodation, in a ski-in/ski-out location with panoramic views over Cervinia. It is located above the village directly on the pistes, with the centre of Cervinia a 15-20 minute walk away, a free shuttle bus is provided. Excellent facilities are available including a restaurant, bar with panoramic terrace overlooking the pistes, lounge and lift. Wellness centre (pay locally) with indoor heated pool, sauna, steam room and whirlpool; massage and beauty treatments available (pay locally). Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the hotel. </p>]]></description>
